N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 65.1 - Applicability

State Regulations

The provisions of this Part apply to White Pond and
adjacent State lands in the town of Kent in Putnam County, to Harwood Lake
multiple use area in the town of Farmersville in Cattaraugus County, to Case

Lake fishing access site in the town of Franklinville in Cattaraugus County, to

New Albion Lake in the town of New Albion in Cattaraugus County and to Allen

Lake in the town of Allen in Allegany County ("areas"). Notes
